_04.png ''Nerve'', Blog-A-Log sex and dating column]</ref> and is currently a syndicated sex columnist for [[Metro International]].<ref>[http://www.metro.us/newyork/keyword/funky-brown-chick/]</ref>
== Education ==
Hines attended [[Illinois State University]], where she received a Bachelor of Science in Sociology, and [[Florida State University]], where she received her Master of Science and she also completed post-graduate education at [[Universiteit van Amsterdam]] and [[New York University]].<ref>[http://feministing.com/2010/05/15/the-feministing-five-twanna-a-hines/] Feministing, May 15, 2009.</ref>
